* Bump slate-react to 0.74.2 (children decorations fix)

* Fix find replace decorator

Decorators shouldn't use the plugin options prop, as they close the
initial version and if the options are updated they never get the
updated version. The editor is a stable reference, it's best to ask for
the options at the time of usage.
